  "Case Study: Three friends all earn $4,000/month. Friend A rents alone ($1,400), Friend B has a roommate ($800), Friend C lives with parents ($200). Each saves all housing savings compared to Friend A. After 5 years invested at 7%, how much more has Friend C accumulated than Friend A (who saves $0 extra)?": "",
